Description

Enter a grand fantasy MMORPG full of magic and wonder based on the Forgotten Runes Wizards Cult. The Runiverse is open to anyone begin your adventure, play, create, own land, and earn your place in the pantheon of legends while owning the things you create. Learn more: https://runiverse.world/

About Forgotten Runiverse Items

Quantum Gifts

These items were earned during our pre-alpha Eve of Memory gameplay event in Nov 2023 and will be revealed as usable items for the full release of the game in Q4. No more Quantum Gifts will ever be minted. They come in four different categories:

  • Mounts: Contain mounts that can be used in game
  • Familiars: Contains familiars that can be used in game
  • Styles: Contains cosmetics that can be applied to equipment in game
  • Blueprints: Contains cosmetic skins that completely alter the exterior and interior of a building on player owned land

Builders Crates

Coming in the August New Foundations build, Builder Crates will be similar to Quantum Gifts (exclusive rewards earned only during this build of the game). They will reveal to be entirely different items from Quantum Gifts. You can earn them through gameplay, getting lucky enough to craft a perfect item, or from the Font of Memories.
